title: I Choose Victorinox - Daniel Humm
transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

My background is from Switzerland and my first knife was Victorinox. Eleven Madison Park is where we express our feelings to food. As a chef, your knife becomes like your hands and your knives are very important. They really are a companion through your career. For me it has really stood the test of time. I love the way it feels in your hand, I love the weight it has, I love how it stays sharp for a long time. I think the knife is there to enhance the food and if you have the tools that you're comfortable with, there's no need to ever change. I am Daniel Humm. I'm the chef of eleven Madison park and I choose Victorinox
